<span id="freeTextContainer7422197795371889154">I would call this urban fantasy only by the skin of it&apos;s teeth. In fact, sci-fi / mystery might be most appropriate. Alternate reality very like this, except that it takes in a Jewish settlement, a carved out area of Alaska, that is going to &quot;revert&quot; to Alaska in the coming year. More about identity and homelands.</span>
